      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "EXTRAVAGANTLY (5) has missed the frame at his last two but did run well three back when third (23.69) in a Grade 6 at Murray Bridge. Better than latest and can atone here. NO EAR TRINDALL (4) lines up here off a comfortable win at Angle Park after jumping from box 8 (19.84). Has the squeeze box to overcome and will need the breaks early. One of main contenders. LIFE OF RILEY (1) produced a modest effort most recently when sixth at Angle Park over 342m behind Vintage Flair (20.46) in a TG1-4W. Placed at his previous run. Has never been out of the placings from five starts out of this box. Worth following up. BIRDWOOD FRANKY (8) can sneak into the finish.",
